actually in Africa in '57,

00:53:04.910 --> 00:53:07.520
meeting with one of the
leaders of the African union.

00:53:07.520 --> 00:53:11.060
And I can just imagine what
that connection was like.

00:53:11.060 --> 00:53:14.060
Back then, they saw each
other as brethren fighting

00:53:14.060 --> 00:53:16.520
for a single goal, right?

00:53:16.520 --> 00:53:18.985
What happened in
the last 50 years?

00:53:18.985 --> 00:53:22.100
And I think that's the
challenge for us in the room,

00:53:22.100 --> 00:53:24.830
in this community,
to say, this is

00:53:24.830 --> 00:53:28.010
Google, what we do here
spreads out into the world.

00:53:28.010 --> 00:53:31.910
And if we can take this
challenge on and take us back

00:53:31.910 --> 00:53:33.450
